        <ol style="padding-left: 20px; color: #555; line-height: 1.8; font-size: 15px;">
            <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Place a sheet of blank white paper on the floor against a flat wall.</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Stand flat on the paper with your heel firmly touching the wall behind you.</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Use a pencil to draw a line marking the longest point of your foot (usually the big toe).</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Use a ruler to measure the distance in centimeters from the edge of the paper to the line.</li>
